CHANGES
=======

v1.0
----

* handle options for no command line
* legend in advanced options now handles no legend, no labeled lines, and changing font size
* fixed segfault when closing from PlotView tab
* fixed/updated printing functions
* fixed pan and zoom for single axes plots
* fixed Plot Edit gui
* Changes for newer matplotlib and wxmpl
* Added scrolling panels to PlotEditFrame
* Added plot edit tool, fixed printing, added interpreter functions, documentation
* Added grid tool and fixed zoom/pan for multiple axes.  Also added menu items for import/export text and get\_data function to interpreter
* initial commit
